  "prompt": "How long will it take for a mi 20000 mah power bank to be delivered if ordered from the official mi website?",
  "response": "The delivery time for a Mi 20000 mAh power bank ordered from the official Mi website can vary depending on several factors, including your location, the shipping method you choose, and the availability of the product. Typically, delivery times range from 2 to 7 business days for standard shipping within the country.\n\nTo get the most accurate estimate, I recommend checking the following on the Mi website:\n\n1. **Product Page:** Look for any specific shipping information mentioned on the product page for the Mi 20000 mAh power bank.\n2. **Checkout Page:** During the checkout process, you'll usually see estimated delivery times based on your shipping address and chosen method.\n3. **Customer Service:** You can also contact Mi customer support directly for the most up-to-date information on delivery times.\n\nKeep in mind that during sales, holidays, or other peak times, delivery might take longer than usual.",
